{"tid":1893411,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"23 Feb 元朗Yoho 失守 - 一宗確診個案","createTime":"2020-02-23T08:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T13:46:11.000Z","uid":62935,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d9fa2597b6c9d35864eb959aed17d51bd473e2","tid":1893411,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"據悉，本港今日（23日）新增2宗初步確診個案，其中1宗為住在元朗YOHO的35歲司機，需中港兩地走。<br />\n<br />\n他在2月8日政府實施「強制檢疫」前去過深圳，2月21日聲稱發燒，到博愛醫院求醫，但沒有入院，至23日經屯門醫院病毒快速測試初步確診後才入院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之，該名男病人至少帶病於社區逗留2日多（詳情按此瀏覽 ）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nyoho 配合埋721 都跌極唔多<br />\n最近Grand Yoho 率先跌破買入價<br />\n其他yoho 系 仲可以企硬幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f58492c29ec7919c752305b490f9487e2450c9","tid":1893411,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"89482f9ce81e1a5a849e701c3de902e0681160e5","tid":1893411,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"2月21日聲稱發燒，到博愛醫院求醫，但沒有入院<br />\n<br />\n博愛急症主管準備受靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95726012ce47908bcac48d936ce692982bacb17f","tid":1893411,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"Yoho~"},{"pid":"524ce771b5c4e7bedc35cf947f26637fd00a24f5","tid":1893411,"uid":104668,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"得個一單，想跌？"},{"pid":"ec71f6d9ce3687acb4864920e50f4bd0625a3caf","tid":1893411,"uid":54946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89482f9ce81e1a5a849e701c3de902e0681160e5","tid":1893411,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"2月21日聲稱發燒，到博愛醫院求醫，但沒有入院<br />\n<br />\n博愛急症主管準備受靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T13:42:36.000Z","msg"